@page "/about"
@attribute [Authorize]
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>About · Countdown to August 5th</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page">

    <!-- Back -->
    <a href="/" class="about-back">← Back</a>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-eyebrow">August 5th, 2026</div>
        <h1 class="about-hero-title">Two people.<br/>One day.</h1>
        <p class="about-hero-sub">
            Somewhere between right now and August 5th, 2026, two people who really
            want to see each other will finally get to start something amazing together — in person.
            This site exists to count every single day, hour, minute, and second until that moment.
        </p>
        <div class="about-heart-row">
            <span class="about-heart">♡</span>
            <span class="about-heart">♡</span>
            <span class="about-heart">♡</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features -->
    <div class="about-section-label">What this site does</div>

    <div class="about-features">

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">🎨</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">A new painting every day</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    Every morning at midnight, an AI finds a holiday being celebrated somewhere
                    in the world and commissions a brand-new oil painting in the style of Bob Ross —
                    generated by Flux 2 Pro, one of the most advanced image models on the planet.
                    No two days ever look the same.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">🌤️</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Painted with real weather</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    Before each painting is created, the site checks the actual weather
                    in Lehi, Utah in real time. Sunny skies, snow, thunderstorms, fog —
                    whatever the weather is outside, it gets painted into the scene.
                    The art literally reflects the world right now.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">⏱️</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Your countdown, your timezone</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    The days, hours, minutes, and seconds shown are calculated in your
                    local timezone — not the server's. Whether you're in California, New York,
                    or anywhere else in the world, the clock counts down to midnight on August 5th
                    exactly where you are.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">🖼️</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">A growing gallery</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    Every painting is permanently archived in the Gallery. You can browse
                    the entire collection, see which holidays each day celebrated, the score
                    Claude gave each painting, and who was viewing from where in the world.
                    Each day is a small piece of this journey.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">▶️</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Timelapse player</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    Inside the Gallery, a built-in timelapse player lets you watch every
                    painting play back in sequence — from the very first day all the way to
                    today. Watch the seasons change, the holidays shift, and the journey unfold
                    painting by painting.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Milestone moments</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    On special countdown numbers — 365 days, 100 days, 50, 25, 10, 5, 3, 2, 1 —
                    the site comes alive with a full-screen celebration. The closer to August 5th,
                    the more dramatic the effect. And as you approach each milestone, a quiet
                    reminder appears to keep you coming back.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">👁️</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Live visitors from around the world</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    A live sidebar tracks who's viewing the countdown right now and where
                    they're visiting from — down to the US state level. Every view is logged
                    and visible inside each gallery entry so you can see exactly who was
                    watching on any given day.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-feature">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">📷</div>
            <div class="about-feature-body">
                <div class="about-feature-title">Personal memories</div>
                <div class="about-feature-desc">
                    Inside any gallery day, you can upload your own photos — memories
                    from that day. They live alongside the AI painting, turning the gallery
                    into a scrapbook of the whole journey, not just the art.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Built with -->
    <div class="about-built">
        <div class="about-section-label">Built with</div>
        <div class="about-tech-row">
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Flux 2 Pro</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Claude Sonnet 4.6</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Blazor Server</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Replicate API</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Open-Meteo</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Proxmox LXC</span>
            <span class="about-tech-chip">Cloudflare Tunnel</span>
        </div>
        <p class="about-built-note">
            Running on a homelab server, painted fresh every day, counting down to one moment.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="about-footer">
        <span class="about-footer-heart">♡</span>
        <span>August 5th, 2026</span>
        <span class="about-footer-heart">♡</span>
    </div>

</div>
